OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'loving and
OL,4,Cdevoted mother' stabbed in front of
OL,5,Cher children in Salford
OL,7,FThe family of a woman stabbed in
OL,8,Ffront of her children in Salford have
OL,9,Fsaid she will be remembered as a
OL,10,F"loving and devoted mother."
OL,12,FPerseverance Ncube, 35, was found by
OL,13,Fher two children on Dukesgate Grove
OL,14,Fin Little Hulton. She had suffered a
OL,15,Fsingle stab wound to the chest and
OL,16,Fdied later in hospital.
OL,18,FIn a statement, her family said: 'It
OL,19,Fis with immense pain that we say
OL,20,Fgoodbye to Perseverance Ncube, also
OL,21,Fknown as Percy to her loved ones.
